capable of reaching distances of 300 to 3400 miles the soviet 
union has 1752 rockets of that range and the united states has 867 
the intermediaterange nuclear forces treaty known as inf 
was signed by reagan and gorbachev on dec 8 and contains the most 
stringent verification procedures in arms control history 
