said in a telephone interview 
they have names identity membership and codes all that is 
used to keep the group together and promote a certain direction 
he said in a telephone interview 
theres a trend for the girls to carry something called a 
carpet knife a razor used to cut carpet professionally and they 
carry it around as their weapon of choice he said 
